            <title>[BOOKKEEPER-332] Add SubscriptionPreferences to record all preferences for a subscription</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BOOKKEEPER-332</link>
                <project id="12311293" key="BOOKKEEPER">Bookkeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add SubscriptionPreferences to record the preferences for a subscription. This jira includes:&lt;br/&gt;
1) add SubscriptionPreferences protocol.&lt;br/&gt;
2) separated preferences from subscription state to decouple infrequent-changed data from frequent changed data (like lastConsumedSeqId).&lt;br/&gt;
3) add backward testing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
